institution: GICC (Generic International Climate Center, Geneva, Switzerland)
source: GICCM1 2002: atmosphere:  GICAM3 (gicam_0_brnchT_itea_2, T63L32); ocean: MOM (mom3_ver_3.5.2, 2x3L15); sea ice: GISIM4; land: GILSM2.5
